john rakolta  wikipedia john rakolta from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search john rakolta personal details born  age – political party republican alma mater marquette university harvard university john rakolta jr is the ceo of walbridge formerly known as walbridge aldinger he was also one of the national finance chairs for mitt romneys  presidential campaign rakoltas wife terry rakolta is the sister of mitts former sisterinlaw ronna romney he was offered the opportunity to be part of a consortium of five detroitarea businessmen to provide a loan to mayor kwame kilpatrick to convince him to resign so that the scandals he had created would end but rakolta declined before it actually happened so the other four went on with it alone rakolta received his bachelors degree in civil engineering from marquette university in  and then studied smaller company management at the harvard business school all four of rakoltas grandparents were immigrants from romania he is the honoraryconsul general  for romania in detroit rakoltas father john rakolta sr – was the head of walbridge aldinger before rakolta rakolta jr began his career at walbridge in  became coo in  and ceo in  rakolta is also on the board of the munder funds since citation needed aside from his work for the romney campaign in  rakolta was a major fundraiser for the bush campaign in  most recently he was state finance chair for gov rick snyder of michigan rakolta served as the chairman of new detroit from citation needed rakoltas daughter lauren rakolta was also a major figure in mitt romneys campaign and previously had worked for mitt romney when he was governor of massachusetts she was the finance director for republican rick snyders campaign for governor of michigan in  in  rakolta supported the marco rubio presidential campaign  referencesedit  building design and construction consultants walbridgcome retrieved    constructorul  may  anamaria luca jurnalul național  john rakolta biography a